Don Knight (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_Knight_(actor) 0 Donald Knight (16 February 1933 – 18 August 1997) was an English-born film, television and stage actor. He worked largely in the United States, and often played tough guys. Donald_Knight ( 16_February_1933 – 18_August_1997 ) was an_English-born_film_,_television_and_stage_actor .
